{"id":6382,"date":"2023-08-03T13:43:25","date_gmt":"2023-08-03T13:43:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.screeningdate.com\/?p=6382"},"modified":"2024-03-30T17:22:59","modified_gmt":"2024-03-30T17:22:59","slug":"cmu-fall-application","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/cmu-fall-application\/","title":{"rendered":"CMU Fall Application 2024 | Apply Now"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>The Canadian Mennonite University, CMU Fall 2024 Application portal for admission is currently open. The general public is hereby notified. The application portal will last till August, 2024 for Canadian Students and May, 2024 for International Students. Details of the application are given as follows.<\/p><div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_64 ez-toc-wrap-center counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-light-blue ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title \" >Contents on This Page<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 eztoc-toggle-hide-by-default' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/cmu-fall-application\/#How_to_Apply_for_CMU_Fall_2024_Admission\" title=\"How to Apply for CMU Fall 2024 Admission\">How to Apply for CMU Fall 2024 Admission<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/cmu-fall-application\/#Steps_to_Apply\" title=\"Steps to Apply\">Steps to Apply<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/cmu-fall-application\/#Check_your_Application_Portal_often_for_Required_Items\" title=\"Check your Application Portal often for Required Items.\">Check your Application Portal often for Required Items.<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/cmu-fall-application\/#Apply_for_Financial_Aid_and_Awards\" title=\"Apply for Financial Aid and Awards\">Apply for Financial Aid and Awards<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p><strong>Table of Contents<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc97155085\">How to Apply for CMU Fall 2024 Admission<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc97155086\">Steps to Apply<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc97155087\">Check your Application Portal often for Required Items.<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc97155088\">Apply for Financial Aid and Awards<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-apply-for-cmu-fall-2024-admission\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Apply_for_CMU_Fall_2024_Admission\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc97155085\"><\/a>How to Apply for CMU Fall 2024 Admission<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Interested applicant for the CMU Fall 2024 Application should visit the link below to <a href=\"https:\/\/enrolment.cmu.ca\/account\/register?r=https%3a%2f%2fenrolment.cmu.ca%2fapply%2f\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">apply<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"steps-to-apply\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Steps_to_Apply\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc97155086\"><\/a>Steps to Apply<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Visit the Application portal on <a href=\"https:\/\/enrolment.cmu.ca\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/enrolment.cmu.ca\/<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Click the create account link to fill out the forms.<\/li>\n<li>Pay a Non Refundable fee of $80 and $150 for Canadian and International Students respectively.<\/li>\n<li>Submit all necessary academic documents on or before the deadline.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"check-your-application-portal-often-for-required-items\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Check_your_Application_Portal_often_for_Required_Items\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc97155087\"><\/a>Check your Application Portal often for Required Items.<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>You may upload an unofficial transcript as part of your application to your application portal.<\/p>\n<p>Original official final transcripts are required for final admission and must be submitted directly from an institution (or mailed or delivered in person).<\/p>\n<p><strong>Send documents to:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Canadian Mennonite University<br \/>\nEnrolment Department<br \/>\n500 Shaftesbury Blvd.<br \/>\nWinnipeg, MB \u00a0R3P 2N2<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Email:\u00a0admissions@cmu.ca<\/strong><\/p>\n<h3 id=\"apply-for-financial-aid-and-awards\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Apply_for_Financial_Aid_and_Awards\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc97155088\"><\/a>Apply for Financial Aid and Awards<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>CMU offers nearly 400 scholarships and bursaries to students. In 2019-20, over 50% of CMU&#8217;s students received some amount of scholarship or bursary funding, so be sure to apply!<\/p>\n<p>Scholarship application deadline is<strong>\u00a0February 28<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p>Bursary\u00a0application deadline is\u00a0<strong>May 31 (international students)<\/strong>;\u00a0<strong>July 20<\/strong>\u00a0<strong>(domestic students)<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"The Canadian Mennonite University, CMU Fall 2024 Application portal for admission is currently open. The general public is&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3110,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[448],"tags":[646],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6382"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=6382"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6382\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=6382"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=6382"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=6382"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}